ea|date=2020-04-06|access-date=2020-04-10}}</ref>\n| Imported case\n| {{flag|Israel}}\n| [[Bucharest]]\n| Male\n| 60\n| A reserve [[police officer]]. He returned from [[Israel]] on February 26 and several days later was admitted to the [[Dimitrie Gerota]] Emergency Hospital with flu-like symptoms, but lied about having travelled. Because of this, a penal case has been opened in his name.<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.digi24.ro/stiri/actualitate/justitie/--1273746 |title=Pensionarul de la MAI care a min\u021bit c\u0103 nu a ie\u0219it din \u021bar\u0103 are dosar penal |date=11 March 2020 |website=Digi24 |language=ro}}</ref> Israel's Minister of Tourism said he stayed in the Palestinian territories.<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.g4media.ro/ministerul-turismului-din-israel-pacientul-17-internat-la-spitalul-dimitrie-gerota-a-fost-cazat-in-teritoriile-palestiniene.html |title=Ministerul Turismului din Israel: \"Pacientul 17\", internat la spitalul Dimitrie Gerota, a fost cazat \u00een teritoriile palestiniene |date=12 March 2020 |website=G4Media}}</ref> [[Super-spreader]]; he infected at least 40 others.<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.digi24.ro/stiri/actualitate/--1274663 |title=Pacientul de la Gerota care a min\u021bit a infectat 13 persoane, ultimele patru confirmate vineri. T\u0103taru: \"Arat\u0103 incon\u0219tien\u021ba acelui om\" |date=13 March 2020 |website=Digi 24}}</ref>\n|-\n! 18\n| rowspan=\"12\" | 10 Mar.\n| {{Failure|Hospitalised}}\n| Local transmission\n| {{n/a}}\n| [[Ilfov County|Ilfov]]\n| Female\n| 31\n| Contact of case #12's girlfriend.\n| rowspan=\"8\" | <ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.hotnews.ro/stiri-sanatate-23712980-23712980 |title=UPDATE \u00cenc\u0103 8 noi cazuri de coronavirus \u00een Bucure\u0219ti. Este cel mai mare num\u0103r confirmat \u00eentr-o singur\u0103 zi. Bilan\u021bul \u00eemboln\u0103virilor a ajuns la 25 la nivel na\u021bional |date=10 March 2020 |website=HotNews.ro |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/we